§7§oYou'll slowly get hungry during your adventures - fortunately the Overworld is full of food! You can gather apples from trees, meat from animals or why not grow your own crops using a hoe?§f§r

To eat a food, select it in your hotbar, then click and hold the right mouse button. Keep the §ehunger bar§f full to regain health when you take damage.

§7§oSome raw foods are better when cooked first on a campfire or in a furnace - your tummy will thank you!§f§r